(6, 2, '2013-07-30 22:15:00', '2013-07-30 22:15:00', '<br><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yjVHN15WdjM/Ufg6hEmUL6I/AAAAAAAABwE/PK5xi2szIKk/s1600/FallFestival.png" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="331" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yjVHN15WdjM/Ufg6hEmUL6I/AAAAAAAABwE/PK5xi2szIKk/s400/FallFestival.png" width="400"></a></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>It\'s that time of year to starting preparing for Paws & Effect\'s </div><div>Fall Festival NADAC dog agility trial. </div><div><br></div><div>Nothing compares to running the brilliantly fast and fun NADAC courses. </div><div><br></div><div>Ready, set, let\'s run. </div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/3049238/Paws%26Effect_September_2013_Trial_Premium.doc">Get your premium here.</a></div><div><br></div><div>Don\'t miss out. Sign up today.</div><div><br></div><div>Download Premium <a href="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/3049238/Paws%26Effect_September_2013_Trial_Premium.doc">(word doc)</a> or <a href="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/3049238/Paws%26Effect_September_2013_Trial_Premium.pdf">(PDF)</a>.</div>', 'Fall Festival - Paws & Effect Dog Agility Competition', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fall-festival-paws-effect-dog-agility-competition', '', '', '2013-07-30 22:15:00', '2013-07-30 22:15:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2013/07/fall-festival-paws-effect-dog-agility-competition.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
