(62, 4, '2012-01-23 21:15:00', '2012-01-23 21:15:00', '<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BFm9fMbHcEc/TwdMW7wZKAI/AAAAAAAAATI/C4U8q2r20Xs/s1600/OHFP%2BFinal.jpg"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-BFm9fMbHcEc/TwdMW7wZKAI/AAAAAAAAATI/C4U8q2r20Xs/s400/OHFP%2BFinal.jpg"></a><br>Please join us for One Heart, Four Paws on Sunday, February 12.  This fundraiser will celebrate the human-animal bond with Luis Montalvan, the author of the New York Times bestseller, Until Tuesday.  Mr. Montalvan, accompanied by his service dog, Tuesday, will speak about his experiences with a service dog and how his life has been enriched.  A book signing will follow.<br><div><br></div><div>For more information about Mr. Montalvan, you may visit his <a href="http://www.until-tuesday.com/">website</a>.</div>', 'One Heart, Four Paws', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'one-heart-four-paws', '', '', '2012-01-23 21:15:00', '2012-01-23 21:15:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2012/01/one-heart-four-paws.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
