(83, 2, '2011-09-15 01:18:00', '2011-09-15 01:18:00', '<div></div><div></div><div></div><div></div><br>This video demonstrates one of the ways in which dogs are taught to put their paws in an exact location to "stack."  When a dog stacks, they hold themselves rigid so that a person who is mobility impaired can place one hand between the dog\'s shoulders to help push themselves into a standing position.<br><br>Way to go Michelle and Valor!  This is, in fact, a throw down!', 'Puppy Raiser Throw Down', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'puppy-raiser-throw-down', '', '', '2011-09-15 01:18:00', '2011-09-15 01:18:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/09/puppy-raiser-throw-down.html', 0, 'post', '', 3),
