(89, 4, '2011-07-13 12:52:00', '2011-07-13 12:52:00', '<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xdNeJzouCVQ/Th2V4U9BtqI/AAAAAAAAARo/-b8v34S97c0/s1600/Tag%2Band%2BKremer.jpg"><img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-xdNeJzouCVQ/Th2V4U9BtqI/AAAAAAAAARo/-b8v34S97c0/s400/Tag%2Band%2BKremer.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>The Iowa National Guard is in the process of bringing home their Soldiers from Afghanistan.  Tag\'s been fortunate to be part of their redeployment, greeting them with tail wags and enthusiasm.  We\'re looking forward to sharing more photos and stories as they become available.', 'A friendly presence at Fort McCoy!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-friendly-presence-at-fort-mccoy', '', '', '2011-07-13 12:52:00', '2011-07-13 12:52:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/07/a-friendly-presence-at-fort-mccoy.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
