(93, 2, '2011-06-21 01:17:00', '2011-06-21 01:17:00', '<div><br></div><div><br></div><br><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PzPMbJ76rFI/Tf_wNs-pJ8I/AAAAAAAAA5M/JKLsOdnmHbk/s1600/photo+3.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PzPMbJ76rFI/Tf_wNs-pJ8I/AAAAAAAAA5M/JKLsOdnmHbk/s400/photo+3.JPG" width="298"></a></div><br><div><br></div><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9-qv2nABhpo/Tf_wWjYmxUI/AAAAAAAAA5U/NdyeTiijKKM/s1600/photo+5.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9-qv2nABhpo/Tf_wWjYmxUI/AAAAAAAAA5U/NdyeTiijKKM/s400/photo+5.JPG" width="277"></a></div><br><div><br></div><br><div><br></div>Paws & Effect service dogs and puppy raisers were invited to attend  the Barnstormers game on Saturday night. In the spot light were Valor,  Anthem, Archer, Tag, Jake and Ryder (the service dogs).  <br><br>They, the service dogs and their puppy raisers, took the field at half-time and were given the spotlight to the applause by the AFL\'s Barnstorming fans. It was quite an honor to be a part of the show on the same evening they were giving props to the National Guard for all their service to our country.', 'A night at the Barnstormers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-night-at-the-barnstormers', '', '', '2011-06-21 01:17:00', '2011-06-21 01:17:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/06/a-night-at-the-barnstormers.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(94, 2, '2011-06-18 12:52:00', '2011-06-18 12:52:00', '<div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-njPwJfaetOM/TfyfErfHayI/AAAAAAAAA5A/Mh87P8rP6vA/s1600/CBWTU.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="320" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-njPwJfaetOM/TfyfErfHayI/AAAAAAAAA5A/Mh87P8rP6vA/s320/CBWTU.jpg" width="239"></a></div>We were able to attend the Muster at the Community Based Warrior Transition Unit at Rock Island Arsenal this past week and what a week it was!  We are very much looking forward to returning in August.', 'A week well spent!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-week-well-spent', '', '', '2011-06-18 12:52:00', '2011-06-18 12:52:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/06/a-week-well-spent.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
