(101, 2, '2011-05-24 14:53:00', '2011-05-24 14:53:00', '<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4biusaAAYoQ/TdvGH4UyUiI/AAAAAAAAA4I/J6huFZQomq8/s1600/RooBday.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="240" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4biusaAAYoQ/TdvGH4UyUiI/AAAAAAAAA4I/J6huFZQomq8/s320/RooBday.jpg" width="320"></a></div><div>We don\'t get to see him too often as he\'s enjoying New Orleans with his raiser, Alexa.  It is always an extra special treat to get photos of Roo.  Here he is, already one!  </div>', 'Happy Birthday, Roo!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'happy-birthday-roo', '', '', '2011-05-24 14:53:00', '2011-05-24 14:53:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/05/happy-birthday-roo.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
