(103, 2, '2011-05-22 17:04:00', '2011-05-22 17:04:00', '<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3R-FY1W4BYM/TdZxvdNRZeI/AAAAAAAAA38/bveiI7zDvtc/s1600/TellyAward.png" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="320" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3R-FY1W4BYM/TdZxvdNRZeI/AAAAAAAAA38/bveiI7zDvtc/s320/TellyAward.png" width="240"></a></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Judging has been completed for the 32nd Annual Telly Awards submissions and Paws & Effect\'s public service announcements received two bronze awards.</div><div></div><blockquote type="cite"><div><div></div></div></blockquote><div>One for the PSA video campaign and another one for copy writing. </div><div><br></div><div>We couldn\'t be more honored to receive this acknowledgment from the Silver Telly Council for the excellent work that Paws & Effect presented.<br><br>Special thanks goes out to Todd Cerveris and Kim Spurlock for producing these very moving PSA\'s.<br><br>We also have to thank the cast, crew and volunteers for the four days of filming that led to these great TV spots with a spectacular message. Click on the "Public Service Announcement" tab to view these for yourself.</div>', '2011 Telly Awards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2011-telly-awards', '', '', '2011-05-22 17:04:00', '2011-05-22 17:04:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/05/2011-telly-awards.html', 0, 'post', '', 2),
