(106, 2, '2011-05-09 12:01:00', '2011-05-09 12:01:00', '<div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-c64HGl_V6wM/TcfXjtNBuZI/AAAAAAAAA3w/GDUbvg4hy84/s1600/Agility+Photos.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="192" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-c64HGl_V6wM/TcfXjtNBuZI/AAAAAAAAA3w/GDUbvg4hy84/s320/Agility+Photos.jpg" width="320"></a></div><div>See us in the <a href="http://www.desmoinesregister.com/apps/pbcs.dll/gallery?Avis=D2&Dato=20110508&Kategori=NEWS&Lopenr=105080803&Ref=PH&Params=Itemnr=1">Des Moines Register</a>!</div>', 'Best Photos of the Weekend', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'best-photos-of-the-weekend', '', '', '2011-05-09 12:01:00', '2011-05-09 12:01:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/05/best-photos-of-the-weekend.html', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(107, 2, '2011-05-06 23:05:00', '2011-05-06 23:05:00', '<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JUyezLZD18k/TcR-Ggc0KuI/AAAAAAAAA3s/mVXDzf2tZ4E/s1600/Logo-color.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JUyezLZD18k/TcR-Ggc0KuI/AAAAAAAAA3s/mVXDzf2tZ4E/s1600/Logo-color.jpg"></a></div><br>It is with great celebration that we share our eligibility to participate in the Combined Federal Campaign!  This designation is awarded to nonprofit organizations that can demonstrate that they are operating within very strict fiscal guidelines and that they have a "substantial local presence" in the community they serve.<br><br>It was no small effort to garner this recognition and a HUGE thanks is owed to Andy Burgraff for the many, many hours he contributed in preparing all the necessary forms and applications.', 'We\'re eligible to participate in the Combined Federal Campaign!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'were-eligible-to-participate-in-the-combined-federal-campaign', '', '', '2011-05-06 23:05:00', '2011-05-06 23:05:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/05/were-eligible-to-participate-in-the-combined-federal-campaign.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(108, 2, '2011-04-29 14:27:00', '2011-04-29 14:27:00', '<div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x9LwCo4fXgI/TbrIs2VrY0I/AAAAAAAAA3g/IjF8GtcrecY/s1600/093-1.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="320" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-x9LwCo4fXgI/TbrIs2VrY0I/AAAAAAAAA3g/IjF8GtcrecY/s320/093-1.JPG" width="240"></a></div><br>Tomorrow, a man who honored fallen Soldiers will himself be honored at the Freedom Center.  Steve Layton, a bagpiper for many local military funerals, passed away suddenly this week.  Here he is pictured with Paws & Effect Liberty at Joint Force Headquarters.<br><br>You may read more about Mr. Layton <a href="http://www.whotv.com/news/who-story-bagpiper-dies-20110428,0,2552351.story">here</a>.', 'Honoring Steve Layton and Liberty', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'honoring-steve-layton-and-liberty', '', '', '2011-04-29 14:27:00', '2011-04-29 14:27:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/04/honoring-steve-layton-and-liberty.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(109, 2, '2011-04-28 18:41:00', '2011-04-28 18:41:00', 'Nothing goes with a nice Chardonnay like a Silver ADDY® Award.<br><br><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yARmaOJ3D98/Tbm0mf4KxdI/AAAAAAAAA3c/zsswOKNVfKw/s1600/photo.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yARmaOJ3D98/Tbm0mf4KxdI/AAAAAAAAA3c/zsswOKNVfKw/s400/photo.JPG" width="298"></a></div><br><br>Paws & Effect received their Silver ADDY® at the AAF (American Advertising Federation) luncheon today at Jasper Winery.<br><br>The depth competition in District 9 was amazing and we are honored to accept this prize for our public service announcements (click on the Public Service Announcement tab to see what all the hallaballoo is all about)<br><br>We again want to thank all of our volunteers, sponsors, and creative team for putting together an incredibly moving message.', 'Silver ADDY® Award', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'silver-addy-award', '', '', '2011-04-28 18:41:00', '2011-04-28 18:41:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/04/silver-addy-award.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(110, 2, '2011-04-27 19:52:00', '2011-04-27 19:52:00', 'It cost an average of $1010.12 per puppy in the Military Litter to have them spayed or neutered, microchipped and updated on their vaccinations (let us not overlook the cost of the surgical removal of one squeaker....)  We aren\'t quite done purchasing Heartguard for the year.<br><br>Thankfully, the insurance will cover some of the costs....', 'Statistically speaking, of course.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'statistically-speaking-of-course', '', '', '2011-04-27 19:52:00', '2011-04-27 19:52:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2011/04/statistically-speaking-of-course.html', 0, 'post', '', 1),
