(207, 4, '2010-07-05 14:07:00', '2010-07-05 14:07:00', '<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TDHnax-i3ZI/AAAAAAAAAMc/CEMH0jrtwaI/s1600/Roo+2.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TDHnax-i3ZI/AAAAAAAAAMc/CEMH0jrtwaI/s400/Roo+2.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TDHnatNe5mI/AAAAAAAAAMU/gCtEYR4fvOE/s1600/Roo+1.jpg"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TDHnatNe5mI/AAAAAAAAAMU/gCtEYR4fvOE/s400/Roo+1.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Roo went to his first vet\'s visit and here\'s what it looked like.<div><br></div><div>He slept.</div><div><br></div><div>Through all of it.</div><div><br></div><div>Really.</div><div><br></div><div>The vet checked his heart really well just to make sure nothing obvious was wrong.  He\'s just relaxed is all.  Clean bill of health.  </div>', 'Roo-schach Test', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'roo-schach-test', '', '', '2010-07-05 14:07:00', '2010-07-05 14:07:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/07/roo-schach-test.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(208, 2, '2010-07-01 13:45:00', '2010-07-01 13:45:00', 'So, how do you pronounce that?<br><br>Roo is our latest addition to the Paws & Effect Service dog fleet. He\'s a charmer. He\'s a sweet heart. He\'s just plain fun.<br><br>', 'Meet Roo!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'meet-roo', '', '', '2010-07-01 13:45:00', '2010-07-01 13:45:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/07/meet-roo.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(209, 2, '2010-06-27 13:26:00', '2010-06-27 13:26:00', 'Had a date with a jetliner!? It was actually a day at the airport with the service dogs. No where else in Des Moines can you get exposed (the dogs) to all the sights and sounds of so many different things. Starting with the parking garage, the automatic doors, the tile floors, escalators, elevators, stair, people, clicking and clacking of roller bags, the lovely smells from the fresh baked cookies, TSA screening, more stairs that you can see through (let me tell you this makes me stumble) and all of that was before we made it to the gate! Once on the tarmac there are a whole new set of stimulation\'s. <br><br>Video One - Escalator Training<br><br><br><br>Video Two - Stair and Rotating Doors<br><br><br><br>Video Three - Getting to board the jetliner! <br><br>', 'A date with a jetliner!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-date-with-a-jetliner', '', '', '2010-06-27 13:26:00', '2010-06-27 13:26:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/06/a-date-with-a-jetliner.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(210, 4, '2010-06-25 21:34:00', '2010-06-25 21:34:00', 'I can\'t explain why I dreamed of Roo, how she\'d visit us each morning, peering in for a treat that she knew was just for her.  And, as dreams do, they bring back to us the memories of a certain time and place.  That time and place for our friends was difficult, and despite our hopes and wishes that things would improve, they continued to deteriorate.  Love had a presence, though, packaged with four paws, a tail and those temporary bilateral scars.<div><br></div><div>Roo, in Hebrew, means friend, companion and neighbor.  A more fitting name would have been impossible to achieve.  To honor those memories, watching two people work through some of the most challenging circumstances they might endure, to see how much a factor love was in so many decisions, we\'ve decided to recognize our newest dog with Roo\'s name.</div><div><br></div><div>Brad and Jen, this one\'s for you!</div>', 'Welcome Service Dog Roo!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-service-dog-roo', '', '', '2010-06-25 21:34:00', '2010-06-25 21:34:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/06/welcome-service-dog-roo.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(211, 4, '2010-06-11 18:12:00', '2010-06-11 18:12:00', '<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TBJ86fvjx9I/AAAAAAAAAMM/XJOQZMOgTh4/s1600/Gabor+%26+Toy+%232+6-2010.JPG"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TBJ86fvjx9I/AAAAAAAAAMM/XJOQZMOgTh4/s400/Gabor+%26+Toy+%232+6-2010.JPG" border="0" alt=""></a><br>I don\'t think I\'ve ever, EVER seen Gabor sleep this hard.  Really.  Not ever.  Could it be that he\'s finally growing up?!?  I dunno, but we\'re gonna find out.  We\'re making plans to place Gabor at the end of August.', 'Just makin\' a point...', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'just-makin-a-point', '', '', '2010-06-11 18:12:00', '2010-06-11 18:12:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/06/just-makin-a-point.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(212, 4, '2010-06-02 23:37:00', '2010-06-02 23:37:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TAbr2ktpzeI/AAAAAAAAAME/v77AYZ5_JPs/s1600/IMG_0780.JPG"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/TAbr2ktpzeI/AAAAAAAAAME/v77AYZ5_JPs/s400/IMG_0780.JPG" border="0" alt=""></a><br>He did such a wonderful job in New York, walking through Times Square with nary a concern, riding the trains, riding the bus and...well...he has just turned into one incredible, remarkable, fantastic dog.  We couldn\'t be happier!  We\'ll be placing him this summer or early fall!<div><br></div>', 'Gabor\'s Growing Up', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gabors-growing-up', '', '', '2010-06-02 23:37:00', '2010-06-02 23:37:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/06/gabors-growing-up.html', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(213, 2, '2010-05-21 21:47:00', '2010-05-21 21:47:00', '<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEELfniGI/AAAAAAAAApU/GIb4AJl_vrk/s1600/Todd+%26+Tag+7.JPG"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEELfniGI/AAAAAAAAApU/GIb4AJl_vrk/s400/Todd+%26+Tag+7.JPG" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEDmCr0eI/AAAAAAAAApM/jyTiF9i-BjM/s1600/Todd+%26+Tag+2.JPG"><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEDmCr0eI/AAAAAAAAApM/jyTiF9i-BjM/s400/Todd+%26+Tag+2.JPG" border="0" alt=""></a><br><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEDOxMcsI/AAAAAAAAApE/e_-o5dWmSzg/s1600/Todd+%26+Tag+1.JPG"><img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_cEDOxMcsI/AAAAAAAAApE/e_-o5dWmSzg/s400/Todd+%26+Tag+1.JPG" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Seems that Tag made his way to Lincoln Center and hooked up with one of the actors (and his puppy raiser) of South Pacific! Both Tag and Todd seem to be happy. How can we tell? Well one is wagging their tails and the other is smiling. We\'ll leave it up to you to decide which is which.', 'Who\'s on Broadway!?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'whos-on-broadway', '', '', '2010-05-21 21:47:00', '2010-05-21 21:47:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/whos-on-broadway.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(214, 2, '2010-05-18 14:54:00', '2010-05-18 14:54:00', '<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_Kqg7mOsKI/AAAAAAAAAos/lo0_rWBBIY0/s1600/Tag+getting+on+bus.jpg"><img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_Kqg7mOsKI/AAAAAAAAAos/lo0_rWBBIY0/s400/Tag+getting+on+bus.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br><span><h1><span><span>Tag boarding a B2 bus in the Marine Park, Brooklyn neighborhood heading to a nearby subway station. He and Nicole are on their way home. </span></span></h1><h1><span>He and Gabor got the maximum exposure in New York City. There were a lot of learnings. </span></h1><h1><span>Tag is hesitant with Buses. </span></h1><h1><span>Gabor shined where we didn\'t anticipate it!</span></h1></span>', 'The "B" is for Brooklyn!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-b-is-for-brooklyn', '', '', '2010-05-18 14:54:00', '2010-05-18 14:54:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/the-b-is-for-brooklyn.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(215, 2, '2010-05-16 16:22:00', '2010-05-16 16:22:00', '<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_AcQZn5utI/AAAAAAAAAoc/Ir4myELqfmo/s1600/tumblr_l2hq69Rx6X1qakfndo1_500.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_AcQZn5utI/AAAAAAAAAoc/Ir4myELqfmo/s400/tumblr_l2hq69Rx6X1qakfndo1_500.jpg" alt="" border="0"></a><br>He\'s finding out that he ain\'t in Iowa anymore.<br><br>Gabor\'s adventures currently has him traveling to New York City. He is getting schooled on the ways of the big  city.<br><br>Check out his expoits on <a href="http://guerilladogs.tumblr.com/">Guerilla Dogs Blog</a>.<br><br>The  picture posted is Gabor on the "B" Train to B\'klyn!', 'Gabor does the Big City.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gabor-does-the-big-city', '', '', '2010-05-16 16:22:00', '2010-05-16 16:22:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/gabor-does-the-big-city.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(216, 2, '2010-05-16 16:17:00', '2010-05-16 16:17:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_Acu24eWdI/AAAAAAAAAok/Wa1FlmG2rhA/s1600/Gabor+Tour+for+Life+2.jpg"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S_Acu24eWdI/AAAAAAAAAok/Wa1FlmG2rhA/s400/Gabor+Tour+for+Life+2.jpg" alt="" border="0"></a><br><br>Gabor has had lots of outings: <div>Hy-Vee, Sams, Kohl\'s, Michael\'s, Factory Card Outlet, Panera\'s  Restaurant, Java Creek Coffee Shop, Iowa Workforce Development ECI  meeting, a two hour workshop on I9 forms and E-Verifying I9 (everyone  got 2 hours continuing credits....add that to his credentials), a two  hour presentation on starting your own business....very boring, a walk  through the fitness gym.<br><br></div> <div> </div> <div>He also goes for two walks a day, without his Halti and does very  well, and to the dog park every day the weather permits.  He goes for   multiple rides in the car every day and is now sharing the back seat  with Allie.  For about the first week he would lay down on the floor in  the back seat.</div> <div> </div> <div>Even got him to go to one specific tree in our yard to relieve  himself.  He got the idea the <strong><u>second! time</u></strong> I  called him to the tree and gave him a treat when he was finished.  This  will save our small plants from turning "yellow".  <strong>;-)</strong></div> <div> </div> <div>He still isn\'t sure of drive up windows (Starbucks, McDonald\'s,  etc.).  Barks at the menu board, the money taker and coffee giver.  Will  work on this.  He\'s just a bit unsure of these.<br></div>', 'What\'s Gabor up to these days?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'whats-gabor-up-to-these-days', '', '', '2010-05-16 16:17:00', '2010-05-16 16:17:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/whats-gabor-up-to-these-days.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(217, 2, '2010-05-11 03:35:00', '2010-05-11 03:35:00', '', 'Tunnel\'s - schmunnels!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tunnels-schmunnels', '', '', '2010-05-11 03:35:00', '2010-05-11 03:35:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/tunnels-schmunnels.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(218, 2, '2010-05-04 21:54:00', '2010-05-04 21:54:00', '<br><br>The agility trial kicked off with a Friday afternoon with a couple courses to get the dogs and handlers warmed up for the main event. Other than the wind we couldn\'t have asked for a better Saturday of trialing. Spring reared it\'s ugliness Sunday afternoon with a nicely formed "Red on the Radar" storm cell that passed just to the west of us. We could have gone without the thunder and lightening but why not mix it up a little bit. We took a break in the show to present Tag and his new handler to the group. We celebrating the placement with cake adorned with Paws & Effect and the MS Society logos. The MS society has contributed to the placement of Tag. Enjoy the video of Tag\'s Last Run.', 'Spring Fling has come and gone.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spring-fling-has-come-and-gone', '', '', '2010-05-04 21:54:00', '2010-05-04 21:54:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/05/spring-fling-has-come-and-gone.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(219, 4, '2010-04-29 12:37:00', '2010-04-29 12:37:00', '<a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S-shCYTsDCI/AAAAAAAAAoM/aqi1AaLm18c/s1600/IMG_0769.png"><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S-shCYTsDCI/AAAAAAAAAoM/aqi1AaLm18c/s400/IMG_0769.png" border="0" alt=""></a><div><span><span><br></span></span></div>From employment workshops to the gym, Kohls, the grocery store, Starbucks, the dog park and SO MUCH MORE, it is the dog\'s life for Gabor.  He\'s a quick learner according to his puppy raisers and we couldn\'t be more proud!  He is slated for placement with a Vietnam veteran who resides in Seattle this fall.  We\'ve got big plans to host a celebration at Delta Society\'s headquarters, sharing the experience with the staff members there.', 'It\'s A Dog\'s Life', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'its-a-dogs-life', '', '', '2010-04-29 12:37:00', '2010-04-29 12:37:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/04/its-a-dogs-life.html', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(220, 2, '2010-04-21 13:42:00', '2010-04-21 13:42:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S88By1qTk8I/AAAAAAAAAnk/jgZGm0j5vTA/s1600/Spring+Fling.png"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S88By1qTk8I/AAAAAAAAAnk/jgZGm0j5vTA/s400/Spring+Fling.png" border="0" alt=""></a><br>No silly, it\'s a dog agility trial. Paws & Effect is hosting our Spring Fling, a NADAC Dog Agility Trial, May 1 - May 2. As an added bonus we will also be running 3 courses on Friday evening.  <a href="http://www.bethann.us/NADAC">Get you premiums here!</a>', 'Spring Fling, if you know what I mean!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spring-fling-if-you-know-what-i-mean', '', '', '2010-04-21 13:42:00', '2010-04-21 13:42:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/04/spring-fling-if-you-know-what-i-mean.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(221, 2, '2010-04-19 03:23:00', '2010-04-19 03:23:00', 'April\'s Fool Fun Run Fun, Run, Fun, Run.<br><br>Can I say that?<br><br><br><br>Paws & Effect hosted the spring "April\'s Fool Fun Run" this weekend at Canine Craze in West Des Moines. As seen in the video, Tag, a service dog, ran a clean Tunnelers run. I had never run Tag through an agility course. I must say he is fast but I am faster!', 'April\'s Fool Fun Run Fun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'aprils-fool-fun-run-fun', '', '', '2010-04-19 03:23:00', '2010-04-19 03:23:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/04/aprils-fool-fun-run-fun.html', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(222, 2, '2010-04-13 18:38:00', '2010-04-13 18:38:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S8S7Ps0j9eI/AAAAAAAAAnc/1-R7IdYA0nc/s1600/Aprils+Fool.png"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S8S7Ps0j9eI/AAAAAAAAAnc/1-R7IdYA0nc/s400/Aprils+Fool.png" border="0" alt=""></a><br>What are you doing this weekend? <div><br></div><div>Well, Paws & Effect\'s Annual <span>April\'s Fool Fun Run</span> has snuck up on us. </div><div><br></div><div>When is it? Funny you should ask. </div><div><br></div><div>It\'s this weekend! April 17, 2010. We are accepting "Day of" entries but our preference is early entries.</div><div><br></div><div>This is an indoor Fun Run at Canine Craze\'s dog training center. Let\'s see you there!</div>', 'April\'s Fool Fun Run', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'aprils-fool-fun-run', '', '', '2010-04-13 18:38:00', '2010-04-13 18:38:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/04/aprils-fool-fun-run.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
