(229, 4, '2010-03-25 15:35:00', '2010-03-25 15:35:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/S6uDL0GDHyI/AAAAAAAAALs/dWdKLzZKlTQ/s1600/bear+2.jpg"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_xIu2b116KkI/S6uDL0GDHyI/AAAAAAAAALs/dWdKLzZKlTQ/s400/bear+2.jpg" border="0" alt=""></a><br>Bear\'s been camera shy lately, literally walking away from the lens.  Goes to show that some things are worth the wait.  Thanks, Chris, for a Bear update.', 'The Lussow\'s Bear!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-lussows-bear', '', '', '2010-03-25 15:35:00', '2010-03-25 15:35:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/03/the-lussows-bear.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
