(231, 2, '2010-03-09 03:12:00', '2010-03-09 03:12:00', '<a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S5W-B9CZk5I/AAAAAAAAAms/RWDB6eGa5a8/s1600-h/photo.jpg"><img src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S5W-B9CZk5I/AAAAAAAAAms/RWDB6eGa5a8/s400/photo.jpg" alt="" border="0"></a><br>We are barely getting the momentum that we want in terms of bringing in the big groups for our Pet Partner training workshop but we can say that we walk out when the class has ended knowing that we are going to have the highest quality teams possible. As they always say, quality over quantity!<br><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S5W-CIC1eEI/AAAAAAAAAm0/52pqNu2bhoU/s1600-h/photo%282%29.jpg"><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_8M0BX0lsHes/S5W-CIC1eEI/AAAAAAAAAm0/52pqNu2bhoU/s400/photo%282%29.jpg" alt="" border="0"></a>Thanks to those that attended the weekend Pet Partner workshop. We know it is a couple days out of your lives but keep in mind that in the end you will put even one smile on a clients face and have brightened little tiny bit of their day you can say that you moved mountains.', 'Pet Partner Training Workshop Weekend.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pet-partner-training-workshop-weekend', '', '', '2010-03-09 03:12:00', '2010-03-09 03:12:00', '', 0, 'http://www.dev.paws-effect.org/wp/2010/03/pet-partner-training-workshop-weekend.html', 0, 'post', '', 0),
